249
00:22:11,396 --> 00:22:13,116
<font color="#ffff00">Mari, Mei-zuo. Bersulang.</font>

250
00:22:15,436 --> 00:22:18,763
<font color="#ffff00">Tunggu, tadi kita bicara sampai mana?</font>

251
00:22:20,664 --> 00:22:23,416
